OL,4,CMillions cannot afford water bills,
OL,5,Csays watchdog
OL,6, More than a million households are
OL,7, struggling to pay their water bills, a
OL,8, consumer group has said.
OL,10,FSome people have even had to skip meals
OL,11,Fto pay for water, the Consumer Council
OL,12,Ffor Water (CCW) said.
OL,14,FIt is calling for a single "social
OL,15,Ftariff", based on a percentage of
OL,16,Fpeople's incomes to lower the costs.
OL,18,FThe government said it would work with
OL,19,Findustry to "build a stronger, better
OL,20,Fand fairer water service for those who
OL,21,Fneed it most".
